<section class="launching-section">
  <div class="launching-inner">
    <p class="launching-eyebrow reveal">Launching with Weather</p>
    <h2 class="launching-h2 reveal" data-stagger="2">Weather ships&nbsp;first.</h2>
    <p class="launching-body reveal" data-stagger="3">Kalshi and Polymarket weather contracts settle on official station data. Observations, forecasts, satellite, and settlement records for every market, cleaned and reconciled to settlement grade. Sports, economics, and more verticals follow on the same&nbsp;SDK.</p>
    <a href="/weather/" class="cta-btn reveal" data-stagger="4">See the weather SDK</a>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .launching-section {
    background: var(--bg-primary);
    padding: 100px 0;
  }
  .launching-inner {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 48px;
  }
  .launching-eyebrow {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: .12em;
    color: var(--text-faint);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  .launching-h2 {
    font-family: 'Funnel Display', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: clamp(32px, 4vw, 44px);
    line-height: 1.15;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: var(--text-heading);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  .launching-body {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.85;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    max-width: 720px;
    margin-bottom: 36px;
  }
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .launching-section { padding: 60px 0; }
    .launching-inner { padding: 0 24px; }
    .launching-h2 { font-size: 28px; }
    .launching-body { font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.7; max-width: 100%; }
  }
</style>
